{"tid":768873,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"(護膚品)我係咪買左問題產品?(有圖)","createTime":"2018-08-05T18:15:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T19:12:25.000Z","uid":84373,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"dd0ac15f82457074f0e9a0d093ccca42012f0310","tid":768873,"uid":84373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T18:15:46.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我最近想買撕除式面膜去清粉刺<br />\n咁我就起旺角SASA問sales有咩推薦<br />\n佢就比左呢隻我 <br />\n<br />\ndaytox peel off mask<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/06/020807_a950aa827753b53c3d531043d7bd128d.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F06%2F020807_a950aa827753b53c3d531043d7bd128d.jpeg&h=3391568a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁我就諗住去試下用<br />\n開左佢之後我發覺要好大力先唧到出黎<br />\n同埋唧出黎之後好乾 好似狗屎咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/06/020928_9d7d3d0472985b1e6657e7dd2fe8e5c7.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F06%2F020928_9d7d3d0472985b1e6657e7dd2fe8e5c7.jpeg&h=f2506882&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/06/020932_3200dce41936e8c2c000785164ea6ebc.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F06%2F020932_3200dce41936e8c2c000785164ea6ebc.jpeg&h=636c985f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同網上完全唔同 網上好水好易搽開<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/06/021007_daa9f1f8cb3b63102cee635d6a1a984b.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F06%2F021007_daa9f1f8cb3b63102cee635d6a1a984b.PNG&h=85ce50c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後完全搽唔到上去 搽到好似抆爛屎咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/06/021501_2858d44d115f9d0bb826fc554498bb1a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F06%2F021501_2858d44d115f9d0bb826fc554498bb1a.jpeg&h=56d61dd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇人有同樣問題?"},{"pid":"81dbcc7f998af4c1c10ec461473616ce70c6b407","tid":768873,"uid":84373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T18:16:39.000Z","msg":"同埋我起旺角買但唔係住果頭<br />\n換貨係咪一定要返果間野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c54baa24a2c7bb0c0044475cec3f661327f8385a","tid":768873,"uid":112909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T18:17:21.000Z","msg":"係咪過咗期㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cdd57e54f1cb2334ac17ee446941dc5fc817177","tid":768873,"uid":84373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c54baa24a2c7bb0c0044475cec3f661327f8385a","tid":768873,"uid":112909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T18:17:21.000Z","msg":"係咪過咗期㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T18:19:56.000Z","msg":"搵唔到有寫日期 但似<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf074ec61203ae720233cf98b9791aa164203a61","tid":768873,"uid":84373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T18:37:59.000Z","msg":"紅撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我有放上臉試搽過 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/06/023729_ac286181f9d7c690c245388c97e49a23.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F06%2F023729_ac286181f9d7c690c245388c97e49a23.jpeg&h=0a3a3c07&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5efbc352cf7a7b1e3ef7b75a32346e5e65792074","tid":768873,"uid":174074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r